Output .vhs/filter.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 700
Set Height 320
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Type "printf 'CandyCore\nCandySprinkles\nHoneyBounce\nSugarBits\nSugarPrompt\nCandyShell\n' | ./bin/candyshell filter --placeholder 'type to filter…'"
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Type "sug"
Sleep 800ms
Down Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 800ms
